### Prerequisites
- Node.js >= 16.0.0
- MySQL >= 8.0
- Redis >= 6.0
- Git

### Backend Setup
```bash
cd backend-api
npm install
cp env.example .env          # Configure environment variables
npx prisma generate          # Generate Prisma client
npx prisma migrate dev       # Run database migrations
npm run dev                  # Start development server
```

### Frontend Setup  
```bash
cd admin-dashboard
npm install
npm run dev                  # Start development server
```

